author: David O'Shaughnessy
title: WTF | Photo: Someone's actually gone and got a Pizza Rat tattoo
text:
The hero New York didn't ask for but deserves will now live on forever on the leg of one brave/idiotic New Yorker.
Reddit user wxcore decided to immortalise everyone's favourite pizza-obsessed rodent on his leg with this piece inked by Kati Vaughn at Magic Cobra Tattoo Society in Brooklyn. Now that's commitment.
View post on imgur.com Via Reddit
